scenes.label: *start
texts: The chopper will be ready in two minutes.
Tsk. Why the hell do I have to go? Just leave it to the army.
The government's orders were for you.
You should comply, even if it's just for show. They're virtually our sponsors, after all.
Who are you to boss me around, you lanky nerd?
I should tell the government where to stick it, too. They must think I'm their dog or something. Those bastards...
I have no idea what's so special about that woman...
...but she can't be more important than my GAIA.
